        [
          "You were embraced in Islamic Spain during the twilight of Arab rule over 500 years ago.  You were a Jewish scholar of the Kaballah and a magical dabbler, but your embrace shatttered your faith. Now you are a scholar of the vampiric Jyhad and the Cainite Hersey, the belief that vampires are behind the great religions of mankind, conditioning for mortals for when vampires openly declare their global domination.  This hersey is an ancient plot and possibly the true core of the Jyhad.  That your faith was a false construction conceived by vampires to further their selfis goals offends you greatly and exposing the truth of the Cainite Hersey drives you.  In the past you were indiscreet and were caught hoarding heretical texts such as the book of nod, it has damaged your standing within the Camarilla but not your zeal."
